title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 239-9.1 - Severability
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 239-9.1 - Severability

State Regulations

Each Subpart of this Part is severable, and in the event
that any Subpart of this Part is held to be invalid, the remainder of this Part
continues in full force and effect. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
239-9.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
